So far, this game is not going well for me. I have played alot of other 40k games like Space Marine and i have gotten perfect graphics and fps, but not in this. The graphics are not optimal and makes me go -10 fps. I can't even go far into the game... I expected more from this game even if it is in Alpha. I have been following this game and it is a disapointment.
My opinion {So Far, may change}
You shouldn't get this game even if you have a well built custom PC. Not optimal and can only garuntee you about 20-50fps with decent computer
This really pulls the whole game down
